    "longBusinessSummary": "Binh Minh Plastics Joint Stock Company manufactures and trades in plastic pipes and fittings for water supply and drainage, telecommunication, electricity, and industrial and civil construction industries primarily in Vietnam. Its products portfolio includes UPVC, HDPE, and PP-R pipes and fittings; HDPE double-wall corrugated pipes, fittings, and rubber seals; rubber seals and solvent cements for UPVC pipes and fittings; and sprayers and protect helmet products. The company also designs, manufactures, and trades molds for plastics and casting industry. In addition, it is involved in the consultation and execution of water supply and drainage works, yards, and services of chemical inspection, analysis, and testing, as well as the trade, import, and export raw materials, chemicals, supplies, machinery and equipment for plastics, engineering, construction, water supply and drainage, and laboratory equipment. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Binh Minh Plastics Joint Stock Company (HOSE:BMP) operates as a subsidiary of Nawaplastic Industries Co., Ltd.",
